in the correctional facilities in all 28 of Alabama's department of corrections.

33:52.403 --> 34:05.155
And we are now, have been invited by the state of Georgia to do the same thing there, everybody.

34:05.175 --> 34:05.335
Come on.

34:05.355 --> 34:10.099
So if Jesus loves the broken, then so will we say it again.

34:10.119 --> 34:16.065
So what do we do with all this?

34:16.085 --> 34:17.106
Let me tell you what you do about it.

34:17.794 --> 34:19.696
You're gonna do the same thing we've been doing for 25 years.

34:20.437 --> 34:23.100
And that is we're not taking that offering.

34:23.261 --> 34:28.807
We teach you this stuff five weeks out so that we don't have you all hyped up, manipulated.

34:29.268 --> 34:36.557
No, no, no, you get to go home for five weeks and plan, prepare, talk to your spouse if you have one, make your own decision.

34:36.897 --> 34:39.601
Each man should give what he's decided and it's hard to give.

34:40.041 --> 34:43.866
Not under compulsion, not being greedy either.

34:44.887 --> 34:47.250
No, for God loves a cheerful giver.

34:47.458 --> 34:52.584
We teach you how not to hear from us, but how to hear from God.

34:54.106 --> 34:57.190
And so I'm going to say the same thing that we've been saying for 25 years.

34:59.553 --> 35:00.054
Ask God.

35:01.135 --> 35:02.036
We're not going to ask you.

35:02.296 --> 35:04.239
We're asking you to ask God.

35:05.160 --> 35:06.942
Lord, what would you have me do?

35:07.303 --> 35:08.544
And there's just nothing more fun.

35:10.667 --> 35:13.170
I can't even think of anything that I would want more for you right now.

35:13.762 --> 35:17.508
Well, having a lost person next to you in church is just exhilarating.

35:19.010 --> 35:22.435
But when you're out there and you say, Lord, am I supposed to?

35:22.896 --> 35:24.899
And then whatever it is, you're at a restaurant, I don't know.

35:25.300 --> 35:25.861
You go, Lord?

35:26.001 --> 35:27.604
And he goes, yes, do it.

35:29.026 --> 35:31.970
And then you, you bless them.

35:34.214 --> 35:35.596
And they go, why?

35:36.437 --> 35:37.299
Why would you do that?

35:38.500 --> 35:42.066
And you say, because it's all for Jesus, I was, I'm on assignment.

35:42.882 --> 35:48.029
by my Creator, an ambassador lets you know you matter to God.

35:49.331 --> 35:50.573
And tears come down their face.

35:52.416 --> 35:55.761
And then you walk out going, who else, Lord?

35:55.821 --> 35:56.522
You know what I'm saying?

35:56.542 --> 35:57.864
Like, oh Lord, yeah.

35:57.884 --> 35:59.086
Because you're hearing from God.

35:59.506 --> 36:00.828
Church, I want you to hear from God.

36:02.571 --> 36:05.675
I want you to ask, how am I asking you to do it?

36:05.695 --> 36:06.396
And I need you to do it.

36:06.877 --> 36:10.482
Between now and December 14th, Lord, what should I do?

36:11.074 --> 36:17.442
And everything we do, every person we reach, every gift we give is all for Jesus.

36:17.982 --> 36:18.763
Let's bow for prayer.

36:19.544 --> 36:20.485
It's a father, thank you.

36:21.266 --> 36:24.770
Thank you for this exciting season when we get to lead people to Jesus.

36:25.551 --> 36:30.417
Have these outreaches, Christmas, Lord, the time to celebrate your birth.

36:31.459 --> 36:35.103
And God welcome all these new people into our auditoriums.

36:36.264 --> 36:41.010
And God for us to do something on the 14th that's gonna echo through eternity.

36:42.754 --> 36:44.897
And Lord, we do it because we love you so much.

36:45.117 --> 36:52.006
And so God, I'm asking that you literally speak to every person who calls Highlands home.

36:53.408 --> 36:55.331
Now with every head bowed and every eye closed.

36:56.252 --> 36:58.816
If you're here today and you say, man, I'm not even close to him.

36:59.797 --> 37:01.559
And I so want to be close to him.

37:02.801 --> 37:12.594
Did you know that you can actually, with one heartfelt prayer, have all of your sins forgiven removed from his memory and he gives you a fresh start?

37:13.538 --> 37:25.532
And honestly, I think this season is really all about that, that we're gonna get close to the Lord and we're gonna know him personally and love him and commit our lives to him.

37:26.433 --> 37:33.242
And maybe if you've done that before and you just somehow, you ended up away from God, I'm asking you to come back.

37:34.283 --> 37:36.485
Or maybe you've never made that decision.

37:36.545 --> 37:40.370
It's always been religion for you and you're ready for a relationship.

37:41.026 --> 37:43.248
Then right there we are whisper these words.

37:43.329 --> 37:45.831
Say, Jesus, I wanna know you.

37:46.953 --> 37:49.816
I wanna be in relationship with you.

37:49.836 --> 37:52.719
I ask you to forgive me of my sins.

37:53.540 --> 37:54.861
Come into my life.

37:55.963 --> 38:04.412
Be the Lord of my life because I believe you are the Son of God who died and rose again.

38:04.432 --> 38:09.618
And today I put my faith in you.

38:10.722 --> 38:11.907
your name I pray.

38:11.967 --> 38:14.699
Amen.

38:14.719 --> 38:18.194
Now how about a hand clap for everybody who just prayed that prayer?

